THE LABORATORY U S WEST is a diversified telecommunications company formed as a result of the breakup of the Bell System. In 1985, U S WEST Advanced Technologies was created to perform R&D for all business units of U S WEST. Advanced Technologies also is responsible for oversight of R&D performed on behalf of U S WEST by Bell Communications Research (Bellcore) and other external organizations (such as universities, equipment manufacturers, software vendors, etc.). Approximately lo15% of the R&D performed internally by Advanced Technologies is focussed on applied research in technology areas deemed critical to the corporationâ€™s future.